### 

#### 


```mermaid
classDiagram
    class PluginManager {
        +plugins: KPlugin[]
        +init()
        +installPlugin()
        +uninstallPlugin()
        +resloveRoutes()
        +resloveEditorExtension()
    }
    
    class KPlugin {
        +name: string
        +routes: RouteConfig[]
        +editorExtensions: ExtensionWrapper[]
        +menus: SiderMenuItemProps[]
        +locales: any
        +services: Services
    }
    
    class PluginConfig {
        +name: string
        +status: string
        +routes: RouteConfig[]
        +globalRoutes: RouteConfig[]
        +menus: SiderMenuItemProps[]
        +editorExtension: ExtensionWrapper[]
        +locales: any
        +services: Services
    }
    
    PluginManager --> KPlugin : manages
    KPlugin --> PluginConfig : configures
```

#### 
Tiptap

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Editor Kit] --> B[]

    A --> D[]
    
    B --> E[]
    B --> F[]
    B --> G[]
    
    C --> H[]
    C --> I[AI]

    D --> L[]

```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 
    participant PM as 
    participant EM as 
    participant Y as Yjs
    participant DB as 
    
    U->>+PM: 
    PM->>+EM: 
    EM->>+Y: 
    Y->>+DB: 
    DB-->>-Y: 
    Y-->>-EM: 
    EM-->>-U: 
```
